{"tid":1743162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集中區選  未來幾日行動係幫手拉票 踢走保皇黨","createTime":"2019-11-21T05:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T06:27:34.000Z","uid":175194,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9761bce531f2507fad8c8308e6d6255f566270fe","tid":1743162,"uid":175194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"大家請諗深一層呢場選舉嘅意義<br />\n呢場係一場公投 <br />\n如果建制大勝就等如民意跟本唔係我地果邊<br />\n到時對家就多一粒大子彈 <br />\n亦比國際睇到我地做嘅野跟本大部份人唔認同<br />\n大家知唔知今次選舉有好多後生仔參選<br />\n就係為左打倒建制派保皇黨 點解我地唔多d支持佢地<br />\n香港人請團結 星期日一定要投票<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f33d17128796d17c6fc10d32183c7007dbf483","tid":1743162,"uid":175194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:46:10.000Z","msg":"集中區選 <br />\n未來幾日行動係幫手拉票<br />\n踢走保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad623fecbe07fb5965d7906101c9731c8050095e","tid":1743162,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:46:22.000Z","msg":"幫手推翻今個星期主線︰<br />\n團結！用你一票絕殺保皇黨 ! <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1737525/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1737525/</a>"},{"pid":"c582d4110ef41b4549686e016141f62a5b8411d3","tid":1743162,"uid":175194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:47:21.000Z","msg":"集中區選 <br />\n未來幾日行動係幫手拉票<br />\n踢走保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa419dac96df549013a72b1c00d44660677db842","tid":1743162,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"區選失敗係政府呢半年黎最怕既野<br />\n直接影響選特首<br />\n變相真普選"},{"pid":"85c356a12e0b9bc9be6793b736f49c63c6ad2a39","tid":1743162,"uid":175194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:47:45.000Z","msg":"集中區選 <br />\n未來幾日行動係幫手拉票<br />\n踢走保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546d096